How to Build a SmartLink firmware in Ubuntu

1. Turn on your ubuntu

2. Build your development environment in ubuntu 
	Type this shell cmd in ubuntu Terminal(warning: Don't use root):
		1)sudo apt-get install gcc g++ binutils patch bzip2 flex bison make autoconf gettext texinfo unzip zip unrar p7zip p7zip-rar p7zip-full sharutils subversion libncurses5-dev ncurses-term zlib1g-dev gawk git-core libssl-dev 

		2)git clone https://github.com/ivotten/SmartLink.git

		3)cd SmartLink && ./scripts/feeds update -a && ./scripts/feeds install -a

		4)make menuconfig 

	After that, choice the The SmartLink board, Application and driver in bulidroot menu;
		1)Target System (Ralink RT288x/RT3xxx)  --->
		2)Subtarget (MT7628 based boards)  --->
		3)Target Profile (SmartLink iot board)  --->
		4)LuCI  --->
			Collections  --->
				<*> luci
			Modules  --->
				Translations  --->
					<*> Chinese (zh-cn)

		5)exit and save

	Then Download the relase files and Build your very own firmware:
		make V=s download  && make V=s  -j 4


How to Build a SmartLink firmware in Mac OS 
1. please go to website https://wiki.openwrt.org/doc/howto/buildroot.exigence.macosx , build up the environment for Mac OS 

2. clone the sourcecode and select the packages you need in menuconfig and build the firmware
	1) git clone https://github.com/ivotten/SmartLink.git
	
	2) cd SmartLink 
	
	3) git checkout MacOS
	
	4)  ./scripts/feeds update -a && ./scripts/feeds install -a
	
	5) make menuconfig
	
	 After that, choice the The SmartLink board, Application and driver in bulidroot menu;
                1)Target System (Ralink RT288x/RT3xxx)  --->
                2)Subtarget (MT7628 based boards)  --->
                3)Target Profile (SmartLink iot board)  --->
                4)LuCI  --->
                        Collections  --->
                                <*> luci
                        Modules  --->
                                Translations  --->
                                        <*> Chinese (zh-cn)

                5)exit and save

        Then Download the relase files and Build your very own firmware:
                make V=s download  && make V=s  -j 4

attention:
	If you build up the firmware in China , you may need a vpn for download the source. Otherwise, you may fail to clone the source from github.

